dc_description_s: REMOTE DOWNLOAD NOT AVAILABLE - please contact data@library.columbia.edu for access. Beijing Provincial Trunk Roads, 2000 is a polyline theme representing provincial trunk roads in Beijing Province in China for 2000.  This data layer is part of the China 2000 Township Census data set produced by the All China Marketing Research Co. and distributed by the University of Michigan, China Data Center.
